title: Jeremy Jones - #gohigher contest
description:
Simply submit your best action shot (photo or short video) via Instagram, Twitter or Direct upload.

Between November 1, 2014 and January 15, 2015 and you could be one of the lucky four chosen to head into the alps with Jeremy. Once there, you'll brush upon your safety skills, hike, and of course make some steep turns.

Winners will be selected by Jeremy and O'Neill.

Stay warm, Stay dry and most importantly stay safe!

Remember to always bring a robe, beacon and shovel and never ski/ride alone.
